						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in the Taluk Office.</hi></p>						

						<p>Rāmachandra—A.D. 1287.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record is dated in the king's regnal <hi rend="bold">year 17, Sarvajit, Kārtika, s11u. 10, Thursday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1287 October 16, Thursday, f.d.t. ·93.</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription seems to commemorate the death of Dāmanāyaka, a hero who died in a fight with Mummuḍi Siṅgeya of Kummaṭa.</p>						

						</summary>
